<doc id="1075892" wikidata="Q3853461" url="?curid=1075892" title="Wave mechanics">
<text>Wave mechanics may refer to:

* the mechanics of waves
* the application of the quantum wave equation, especially in position and momentum spaces
* the resonant interaction of three or more waves, which includes the &quot;three-wave equation&quot;

== See also ==
* Quantum mechanics
* Wave equation
* Quantum state
* Matter wave

