<doc id="1075942" wikidata="Q5346745" url="?curid=1075942" title="Edwin Perry">
<text>Edwin Jock Perry is a New Zealand politician. He was a New Zealand First Member of Parliament from 2002 to 2005.

==Member of Parliament==

He was first elected to Parliament as a list MP in the 2002 election, having also stood in the Wairarapa electorate. He formerly held office in the National Party&#x27;s organisational wing. Before entering politics, he worked in marketing. He lost his seat in the 2005 election.

